1
00:00:58,085 --> 00:01:01,061
=Within The Grip=

2
00:01:01,061 --> 00:01:03,031
=Episode 10=

3
00:01:03,031 --> 00:01:07,053
(Zhaoxi is Dead)

4
00:02:07,879 --> 00:02:10,400
You paint the plum blossoms
so well, dear.

5
00:02:11,639 --> 00:02:12,759
You like them, dear?

6
00:02:14,479 --> 00:02:15,120
Master.

7
00:02:25,479 --> 00:02:26,159
How did it go?

8
00:02:27,120 --> 00:02:29,719
No one approached that room
in the past three days.

9
00:02:29,879 --> 00:02:31,919
The stone chest remains closed.

10
00:02:32,520 --> 00:02:35,039
I thought the contact hadn't arrived.

11
00:02:35,639 --> 00:02:38,520
Fortunately, you sprinkled
butterfly lure powder on the ledger.

12
00:02:39,000 --> 00:02:42,039
I released the silver butterfly
when it was agitated.

13
00:03:10,759 --> 00:03:13,240
(It led me
to the Right Chancellor's mansion.)

14
00:03:14,439 --> 00:03:16,319
Shall we wrap it up, Master?

15
00:03:20,319 --> 00:03:21,000
Not yet.

16
00:03:22,120 --> 00:03:26,199
Didn't you see someone
near the secret chamber?

17
00:03:28,000 --> 00:03:29,240
I'll keep an eye on that.

18
00:03:30,840 --> 00:03:31,800
One more thing.

19
00:03:32,000 --> 00:03:34,719
I ran into Miss Xuanji's subordinates
on my way back.

20
00:03:35,159 --> 00:03:36,960
They said she wanted to see you

21
00:03:37,479 --> 00:03:39,439
at Zuixian Building right now

22
00:03:39,840 --> 00:03:40,840
to tell you something.

23
00:03:41,360 --> 00:03:42,199
Zuixian Building?

24
00:03:47,488 --> 00:03:50,048
(Zuixian Building)

25
00:04:00,039 --> 00:04:01,879
- Sister.
- Welcome.

26
00:04:02,960 --> 00:04:04,280
So this is Zuixian Building?

27
00:04:04,919 --> 00:04:06,599
It's been so long since I last saw you.

28
00:04:08,280 --> 00:04:08,780
Yuluo.

29
00:04:09,000 --> 00:04:10,199
I've missed you so much.

30
00:04:10,639 --> 00:04:12,400
He invited us here and ditched us?

31
00:04:12,599 --> 00:04:13,400
Exactly.

32
00:04:16,360 --> 00:04:17,360
What are you doing here?

33
00:04:17,839 --> 00:04:18,720
To see someone.

34
00:04:25,560 --> 00:04:27,759
Yuluo.

35
00:04:28,319 --> 00:04:31,000
Physician Qin,
Xuanji Pavilion, Zuixian Building.

36
00:04:31,399 --> 00:04:32,920
I don't know what you're after,

37
00:04:33,519 --> 00:04:35,879
but you can bring me along.
I can protect you.

38
00:04:37,959 --> 00:04:40,560
I also heard about the burglary
at Xuanji Pavilion last night.

39
00:04:40,959 --> 00:04:43,639
But I never stepped out
of my courtyard all night.

40
00:04:44,240 --> 00:04:47,439
Are you suspecting me
or trying to probe?

41
00:04:48,000 --> 00:04:48,500
I...

42
00:04:51,439 --> 00:04:52,040
Yuluo.

43
00:04:55,120 --> 00:04:57,120
You know that's not what I meant.

44
00:05:11,959 --> 00:05:13,439
Guards. Arrest them.

45
00:05:14,199 --> 00:05:14,699
Go.

46
00:05:17,600 --> 00:05:18,160
Stop.

47
00:05:18,800 --> 00:05:20,680
Are you alright? Are you hurt?

48
00:05:21,319 --> 00:05:22,040
I'm fine.

49
00:05:22,199 --> 00:05:23,079
He's injured.

50
00:05:26,000 --> 00:05:27,480
You seem to be in high spirits.

51
00:05:27,839 --> 00:05:30,360
When will you play chess
with your eldest brother?

52
00:05:33,839 --> 00:05:35,720
If you merely want to play chess,

53
00:05:35,959 --> 00:05:38,920
surely many people
in this courtyard would oblige.

54
00:05:40,879 --> 00:05:43,959
Where is the death guard
you always keep by your side?

55
00:05:46,519 --> 00:05:49,680
You truly don't know where she went?

56
00:05:50,000 --> 00:05:53,399
He's a grown man.
A small cut won't kill him.

57
00:05:54,399 --> 00:05:57,120
Assassins don't come here for no reason.

58
00:05:57,759 --> 00:05:59,519
I'll look into everyone who came.

59
00:06:00,639 --> 00:06:03,319
Why did you two come here today?

60
00:06:04,680 --> 00:06:05,800
Didn't you invite me over?

61
00:06:06,199 --> 00:06:06,920
Me?

62
00:06:23,199 --> 00:06:24,360
How would I know?

63
00:06:25,560 --> 00:06:28,600
What brings you to the Fufeng Pavilion?

64
00:06:28,959 --> 00:06:30,519
If this is merely a casual visit,

65
00:06:31,439 --> 00:06:34,160
I'm afraid I can't entertain you
due to my poor health.

66
00:06:36,120 --> 00:06:38,240
Xuanji caught some assassins
in her courtyard.

67
00:06:40,600 --> 00:06:43,328
Was she hurt?

68
00:06:45,088 --> 00:06:46,079
She's fine.

69
00:06:47,000 --> 00:06:50,279
But those assassins were the same ones
from the Lantern Festival attack.

70
00:06:51,120 --> 00:06:54,160
They confessed
that you were the mastermind

71
00:06:55,120 --> 00:06:56,639
who orchestrated the attacks.

72
00:06:57,120 --> 00:06:58,879
You paid them off with the jade pendant

73
00:06:59,199 --> 00:07:01,639
to assassinate Xuanji
during the Lantern Festival.

74
00:07:02,160 --> 00:07:04,040
I didn't want to make it public.

75
00:07:04,600 --> 00:07:06,000
But Xuanji was in danger.

76
00:07:06,800 --> 00:07:09,720
I reported to the authorities
after I caught the assassins.

77
00:07:10,000 --> 00:07:13,279
Since there is solid proof,
even I can't shield you.

78
00:07:14,160 --> 00:07:16,240
Master Zhaoxi, please come with us.

79
00:07:17,079 --> 00:07:19,040
Chaosheng, what's going on?

80
00:07:29,079 --> 00:07:31,680
Zhaoxi lost his pendant
when he was under attack.

81
00:07:33,160 --> 00:07:35,920
If the assassins in Xuanji's courtyard
carried that pendant,

82
00:07:36,800 --> 00:07:39,759
doesn't that prove
they're the same people?

83
00:07:40,240 --> 00:07:41,240
They failed to kill him,

84
00:07:42,279 --> 00:07:43,360
so they're framing him.

85
00:07:43,639 --> 00:07:46,079
Don't you see
what's happening, Chaosheng?

86
00:07:46,680 --> 00:07:47,439
Or...

87
00:07:47,439 --> 00:07:48,680
What are you implying?

88
00:07:49,600 --> 00:07:51,759
The authorities will
determine right and wrong.

89
00:07:52,519 --> 00:07:56,759
If someone framed Zhaoxi,
the authorities will clear his name.

90
00:07:59,160 --> 00:08:02,240
He needs rest
to recover from his injuries.

91
00:08:03,480 --> 00:08:05,519
He's also a victim here.

92
00:08:06,600 --> 00:08:07,759
The two of us

93
00:08:08,160 --> 00:08:12,040
protected Xuanji from the assassins
during the Lantern Festival gathering.

94
00:08:12,800 --> 00:08:14,839
How could he be the mastermind?

95
00:08:17,240 --> 00:08:20,360
Officers, please go back.

96
00:08:22,360 --> 00:08:22,959
What's wrong?

97
00:08:23,600 --> 00:08:26,519
Are you saying
these officers won't do him justice?

98
00:08:26,839 --> 00:08:30,199
My husband is frail
and just survived an assassination.

99
00:08:30,519 --> 00:08:32,840
This trip would be too much for him.

100
00:08:42,559 --> 00:08:43,759
Quit overthinking, Yuluo.

101
00:08:44,000 --> 00:08:45,960
Zhaoxi seems to be much better.

102
00:08:46,360 --> 00:08:47,639
If you keep obstructing this,

103
00:08:48,000 --> 00:08:51,360
the authorities
might start suspecting us.

104
00:08:51,720 --> 00:08:53,399
Didn't you get what I meant?

105
00:08:54,440 --> 00:08:58,600
I meant to say
that no one shall take anyone away

106
00:09:01,200 --> 00:09:04,519
from the Fufeng Pavilion today.

107
00:09:19,399 --> 00:09:21,480
Don't worry. I'll be right back.

108
00:09:35,120 --> 00:09:36,440
Master, do you need me to...

109
00:09:36,440 --> 00:09:39,159
Fetch my jewelry box.
I'm going to the yamen.

110
00:09:40,519 --> 00:09:41,039
Understood.

111
00:09:52,440 --> 00:09:54,320
We'll interrogate the assassins.

112
00:09:54,440 --> 00:09:55,840
I've spoken to the officers.

113
00:09:55,960 --> 00:09:57,440
They won't expose your identity.

114
00:09:57,639 --> 00:10:00,600
That ledger ended up
exactly where you predicted.

115
00:10:00,679 --> 00:10:03,360
The Right Chancellor
invited Princess Shang over right away.

116
00:10:04,159 --> 00:10:06,519
But before Princess Shang even arrived,

117
00:10:06,519 --> 00:10:10,120
I had delivered the ledger
to General Shen.

118
00:10:44,639 --> 00:10:46,679
This is evidence
of Princess Shang's crimes.

119
00:10:55,039 --> 00:10:58,639
General Shen and some ministers
impeached Princess Shang this morning.

120
00:10:58,919 --> 00:11:01,320
This time,
she won't be able to turn the tide.

121
00:11:01,759 --> 00:11:02,799
Were you spotted?

122
00:11:03,360 --> 00:11:05,320
Almost. Thankfully, I was quick-witted.

123
00:11:05,720 --> 00:11:08,279
That shadow
clinging to your wife is relentless.

124
00:11:08,960 --> 00:11:11,519
Right, the general asks
when you plan to return.

125
00:11:11,559 --> 00:11:14,120
He suggests you send word back first

126
00:11:14,279 --> 00:11:16,440
and let that person know you're alright.

127
00:11:19,159 --> 00:11:22,240
Also, those who went
after the bandits returned.

128
00:11:22,440 --> 00:11:23,879
The scouts said

129
00:11:24,639 --> 00:11:27,679
that the bandits confessed
to assassinating you and Gu Zhaoxi.

130
00:11:27,919 --> 00:11:29,840
They said Gu Zhaoxi died on the spot.

131
00:11:30,519 --> 00:11:32,000
(His body was dumped in a wolf pit)

132
00:11:32,120 --> 00:11:33,639
(and was gnawed down to bare bones.)

133
00:11:39,120 --> 00:11:40,720
How's my uncle doing?

134
00:11:42,200 --> 00:11:43,519
He is in excellent health.

135
00:11:43,600 --> 00:11:45,600
Master, when are you planning to return?

136
00:11:49,559 --> 00:11:51,840
Aren't we doing fine here?

137
00:11:53,080 --> 00:11:56,480
Please stop kidding, Master.
This can't compare...

138
00:11:57,879 --> 00:12:01,399
Y-You couldn't have fallen for...

139
00:12:04,000 --> 00:12:06,159
Zuixian Building's been overrun
with dubious people.

140
00:12:06,480 --> 00:12:09,720
I might as well send you undercover
as a male dancer.

141
00:12:10,639 --> 00:12:12,919
Please don't. I'm sorry.

142
00:12:13,960 --> 00:12:15,559
Speaking of your "wife",

143
00:12:16,919 --> 00:12:19,240
I mean Gu Zhaoxi's wife...

144
00:12:19,519 --> 00:12:21,480
She brought a jewelry box
to bail you out.

145
00:12:22,120 --> 00:12:23,399
To avoid suspicion,

146
00:12:23,480 --> 00:12:26,159
I told those people to accept the bribe.

147
00:12:26,200 --> 00:12:29,080
They'll "release" you because of that.

148
00:12:29,759 --> 00:12:30,559
Where is she?

149
00:12:31,799 --> 00:12:34,279
Probably still outside the yamen.

150
00:12:39,120 --> 00:12:40,679
You're definitely into her.

151
00:12:47,072 --> 00:12:51,624
(Capital Yamen)

152
00:12:59,559 --> 00:13:00,120
Dear.

153
00:13:19,080 --> 00:13:21,120
Didn't I tell you to wait at home?

154
00:13:21,320 --> 00:13:22,240
I was concerned.

155
00:13:26,960 --> 00:13:28,559
How long have you waited here?

156
00:13:32,159 --> 00:13:33,080
Not long.

157
00:13:35,960 --> 00:13:38,360
I heard that you gave them

158
00:13:38,720 --> 00:13:40,840
a box of jewelry to bail me out.

159
00:13:41,559 --> 00:13:43,279
You were implicated because of me.

160
00:13:43,440 --> 00:13:46,080
I had to get you out, no matter what.

161
00:13:46,879 --> 00:13:48,639
Those trinkets mean nothing.

162
00:13:49,759 --> 00:13:51,840
Every young lady cares about her jewels.

163
00:13:52,480 --> 00:13:55,639
They're only worldly possessions to me,

164
00:13:55,840 --> 00:13:58,000
only useful
for the Xuanji Pavilion's missions.

165
00:13:59,879 --> 00:14:01,360
Why did you bail me out?

166
00:14:08,240 --> 00:14:10,279
Your identity is fabricated.

167
00:14:10,840 --> 00:14:12,360
If they find out about it,

168
00:14:13,519 --> 00:14:16,480
it may cause us trouble.

169
00:14:20,000 --> 00:14:20,639
That's all?

170
00:14:23,200 --> 00:14:23,700
Of course.

171
00:14:26,759 --> 00:14:30,240
I thought you bailed me out
because you couldn't bear

172
00:14:30,240 --> 00:14:31,360
to leave me suffering.

173
00:14:34,639 --> 00:14:35,240
Let's go.

174
00:14:54,399 --> 00:14:54,960
Dear.

175
00:15:07,080 --> 00:15:08,120
What's going on?

176
00:15:09,240 --> 00:15:12,639
You didn't even tend your wound.

177
00:15:25,759 --> 00:15:27,440
I'll do it myself later.

178
00:15:30,960 --> 00:15:32,840
I applied your medicine last time.

179
00:15:33,080 --> 00:15:33,960
What's wrong now?

180
00:15:35,679 --> 00:15:36,480
Could it be

181
00:15:37,519 --> 00:15:38,600
that you're shy?

182
00:15:43,679 --> 00:15:44,759
Of course not.

183
00:15:46,360 --> 00:15:49,080
Very well. Let's proceed, dear.

184
00:15:51,072 --> 00:15:53,408
♪Longing lingers within my heart♪

185
00:15:53,408 --> 00:16:00,108
♪Zither strings sigh
for the sorrow parting♪

186
00:16:00,108 --> 00:16:06,880
♪Past tales nest in my soul♪

187
00:16:06,880 --> 00:16:14,016
♪Affection lingers, unforgettable♪

188
00:16:14,016 --> 00:16:18,400
♪Ink-stained scrolls recall bygones♪

189
00:16:18,400 --> 00:16:21,024
♪Each stroke holds a thought♪

190
00:16:21,024 --> 00:16:27,658
♪Prosperity fades like dreams♪

191
00:16:27,658 --> 00:16:34,208
♪With nothing but memories left♪

192
00:16:45,120 --> 00:16:47,279
How did you get that scar?

193
00:16:50,112 --> 00:16:51,086
(Vast Mind, Eternal Will)

194
00:17:00,000 --> 00:17:01,799
Master Wenshuang, you can't enter.

195
00:17:10,640 --> 00:17:11,480
Wenshuang.

196
00:17:16,960 --> 00:17:18,440
Do you know what you're doing?

197
00:17:18,440 --> 00:17:21,319
He's not Zhaoxi. Zhaoxi is dead.

198
00:17:22,240 --> 00:17:23,119
What did you say?

199
00:17:23,400 --> 00:17:24,599
Zhaoxi is dead.

200
00:17:25,559 --> 00:17:26,799
The officers are back.

201
00:17:27,480 --> 00:17:30,440
Those bandits
confessed to every atrocity.

202
00:17:31,440 --> 00:17:34,599
They stopped Zhaoxi's carriage
and robbed him.

203
00:17:35,279 --> 00:17:37,160
They then threw him into the wolf pit.

204
00:17:37,799 --> 00:17:40,119
He was eaten alive by vicious wolves.

205
00:17:40,519 --> 00:17:42,039
The authorities are outside.

206
00:17:42,200 --> 00:17:45,160
The bandits confessed
to assassinating you and Gu Zhaoxi.

207
00:17:45,359 --> 00:17:47,319
They said Gu Zhaoxi died on the spot.

208
00:17:47,720 --> 00:17:49,200
His body was dumped in a wolf pit

209
00:17:49,279 --> 00:17:50,720
and was gnawed down to bare bones.

210
00:17:52,960 --> 00:17:56,240
This man is suspicious.
He might have colluded with...

211
00:17:57,119 --> 00:17:57,759
Wenshuang.

212
00:17:59,599 --> 00:18:00,880
Where are the authorities?

213
00:18:01,279 --> 00:18:02,240
In the front hall.

214
00:18:04,640 --> 00:18:08,119
You've exhausted yourself today.
Stay and rest, dear.

215
00:18:09,240 --> 00:18:10,319
I'll be right back.

216
00:18:37,759 --> 00:18:39,880
Yuluo, are we leaving just like this?

217
00:18:40,680 --> 00:18:43,640
What if that imposter escapes?

218
00:18:43,759 --> 00:18:46,359
Wenshuang, he is your third brother.

219
00:18:46,839 --> 00:18:49,599
I brought him back.
How could I be mistaken?

220
00:18:50,880 --> 00:18:54,240
Exactly, you brought him back.

221
00:18:55,720 --> 00:18:57,880
Isn't the disguise technique

222
00:18:58,119 --> 00:18:59,319
what you excel...

223
00:18:59,319 --> 00:19:01,559
Master Wenshuang, what are you implying?

224
00:19:01,960 --> 00:19:05,079
Are you trying to say
that I killed my husband?

225
00:19:06,599 --> 00:19:07,839
I never said that.

226
00:19:08,880 --> 00:19:11,599
It's just that
the Gu family isn't very close.

227
00:19:12,319 --> 00:19:13,599
I grew up away from home.

228
00:19:13,839 --> 00:19:15,119
Chaosheng travels for business.

229
00:19:15,640 --> 00:19:17,759
Xuanji studies poison arts
with the Medicine King.

230
00:19:18,519 --> 00:19:21,039
Zhaoxi remained housebound
due to chronic illness.

231
00:19:22,440 --> 00:19:24,599
We met at Xuanji Pavilion as children.

232
00:19:24,920 --> 00:19:25,799
You know

233
00:19:27,720 --> 00:19:31,680
that I can try to be the family head
if that's what you want.

234
00:19:31,799 --> 00:19:32,720
Master Wenshuang.

235
00:19:34,640 --> 00:19:37,160
Since you're so straightforward,

236
00:19:37,640 --> 00:19:39,400
let me make things clear.

237
00:19:40,480 --> 00:19:42,680
I brought Zhaoxi back.

238
00:19:43,079 --> 00:19:46,440
He's been traveling and staying with me.

239
00:19:48,119 --> 00:19:50,960
How could I fail to tell
if he's my husband?

240
00:19:51,759 --> 00:19:52,640
Master Wenshuang.

241
00:19:53,559 --> 00:19:57,079
There has never been romance between us.

242
00:19:57,960 --> 00:19:59,599
I'm your third sister-in-law now.

243
00:19:59,880 --> 00:20:01,799
It will remain this way forever.

244
00:20:38,288 --> 00:20:43,351
♪Willows sway in the twilight breeze♪

245
00:20:43,888 --> 00:20:49,209
♪Ancient alleys guard time's secrets♪

246
00:20:49,776 --> 00:20:56,404
♪Bluestones bear life's imprints♪

247
00:20:56,404 --> 00:21:01,168
♪Falling petals, endless longing♪

248
00:21:01,168 --> 00:21:03,504
♪Longing lingers within my heart♪

249
